options.systemMessage:
Classify conversation status by counting messages and checking last sender.

STATUS:
new: 1 message only (user, no support reply)
waiting: 2+ messages, last from support with question
solved: 2+ messages, last from support with solution OR user confirms ("thanks","perfect","works","resolved")
reopened: User says "again","still not working","same issue","happening again"

EXAMPLES:
[user:"Can't log in"] -> {"status":"new","confidence":0.95}
[user:"Not working", support:"What error do you see?"] -> {"status":"waiting","confidence":0.95}
[user:"Not working", support:"Try this: link"] -> {"status":"solved","confidence":0.9}
[user:"Problem X", support:"Fixed", user:"Thanks!"] -> {"status":"solved","confidence":0.95}
[user:"Problem X", support:"Fixed", user:"Still not working"] -> {"status":"reopened","confidence":0.95}

OUTPUT: {"status":"string","confidence":0.0-1.0}

